Mixed database formed.py: form a new databasse with 70% virtual data from the original virtual dataset, and 30% Real data from the original original dataset
data preparation.py: preprocess the mixed database， produce x_windows.npy and get  ready for models' training
100k x_windows form.py: form x_windows_100k.npy 
100k data augmentation.py: augment data to 100k

models folders: 100k and 35040 dataset model training
